Hello and welcome to Odonto.me!

If you haven't already, you can go to http://my.odonto.me/practice
and login with your email address and password to start
setting up your practice

- You can start by customizing your settings like
  preferred language and currency.

- Add users that can access your account (say an 
  assistant) or change your first and last name (you
  are initially named 'Administrator User').

- Add the doctors who will treat your patients.

Please don't ever hesitate to contact us if you need
anything.

